<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We have a policy of constantly improving our services, and for that, we can modify or terminate any of our services anytime. We may change any function, feature, or can terminate our services altogether. This may cause the deletion of user data. Any loss or compromisation of data will not be liable to Pocket Scanner, users are advised to keep their sensitive information outside of the app. We do not promise anything about our services.</span></p>
